data.description: The possibilities are endless with this lovely, spacious home that offers two separate living areas making it perfect for extended living, a home office or rental inc. Situated on a generous piece of land this property provides ample space for gardening, and outdoor activities. The large, heated garage with shop area is perfect for the hobbyist. There is also a metal pole carport for your RV/ Boat and not to be missed is the adorable artist studio. You’ll love the beautiful wood ceilings, and the wood burning stove along with hardwood floors on the main level. The recently added flex space, the newer heat pump, metal roof and newer kitchen appliances are just a few of the upgrades this lovely home offers. Great location and a must see!
